{"id": 2010, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X闲鱼】你都曾经因为什么原因买过/卖过什么样的闲置？", "description": "别让物品闲着，发挥它的最大价值，说不定还有奇妙缘分。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 10913, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171115191553rY728tQuxM3opmKH.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-16T03:00:22Z", "options": [{"id": 249346, "content": "二手电子产品首选啊。淘到很多成色很棒的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 424568}, {"id": 249347, "content": "卖大码球鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142918}, {"id": 252419, "content": "带个翅膀，还拿着弓箭乱射的小屁孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121412}, {"id": 249348, "content": "卖是没钱，买也是没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972458}, {"id": 249349, "content": "旧书，挂画，画画人体模型等", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498762}, {"id": 249350, "content": "独轮车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 823269}, {"id": 251913, "content": "哎哟，不错哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199162}, {"id": 249610, "content": "我都闲了二十几年了，也没人来买我", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186359}, {"id": 249611, "content": "买各种大牌高跟鞋、口红、彩妆、饰品、裙子…然而我是个穿球鞋T恤的女生", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855480}, {"id": 249615, "content": "买错了，又不能退", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016807}, {"id": 249360, "content": "储存盒 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789546}, {"id": 250128, "content": "满满情怀的二手iPhone5 和 一台kindle", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186567}, {"id": 249362, "content": "卖过飞耐时1，小布。一个更新换代，一个没时间骑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185536}, {"id": 249363, "content": "低价买过原装未拆封kindle", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677576}, {"id": 249367, "content": "相机", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356847}, {"id": 249368, "content": "。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136220}, {"id": 249369, "content": "没有我现在太穷了_(:з)∠)_", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058421}, {"id": 249628, "content": "手机壳", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186615}, {"id": 249373, "content": "扫地机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173153}, {"id": 249629, "content": "卖过ZUK Z1，因为Z2当时出了。结果现在手机厂都倒闭了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186614}, {"id": 249632, "content": "我可以卖命嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178534}, {"id": 254241, "content": "爱豆的专辑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202417}, {"id": 249378, "content": "便宜，用最低的钱买到最好的东西！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185585}, {"id": 249634, "content": "电动车?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186634}, {"id": 249379, "content": "当当阅读器", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185587}, {"id": 249636, "content": "烦恼与忧虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186649}, {"id": 254244, "content": "一时心血来潮买了个nokia 老功能机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146774}, {"id": 249381, "content": "难道不是因为没钱了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185592}, {"id": 249637, "content": "卖过一个全新闲置的5升户外野营锅，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149680}, {"id": 249382, "content": "爱过，再见，谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155587}, {"id": 249383, "content": "不爱玩的1、2、Switch游戏，蜜汁尴尬，赶紧出掉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940827}, {"id": 249384, "content": "吃土买的爱豆周边，又因为吃土卖了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142527}, {"id": 249640, "content": "买过早已停产的一些稀有的Swatch，闲鱼和eBay都买过。为什么买二手货？因为没有新的啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186479}, {"id": 249386, "content": "看着尴尬 放着嘛碍地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926895}, {"id": 249642, "content": "易物怡情，是件很好的事，可是听说有很多二手衣物来自太平间，骇人听闻，只是听说……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186684}, {"id": 249387, "content": "通过闲鱼给我的猫找到了新主人，感觉他现在过得比跟我一起的时候幸福。", "image": "img/option/option/20171116221306cMkUuyB2nJ6L9wK7.jpg", "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759228}, {"id": 249643, "content": "我倒没事没啥怕的，我有个哥们是卖人骨嘎巴啦佛宝的，他说出处干净，听着也是很怕怕的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186684}, {"id": 254763, "content": "卖掉了用了一半的护肤品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207562}, {"id": 249388, "content": "各种你懂的的绝版书记", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244095}, {"id": 249644, "content": "音乐，录音室，吉他，效果器，交友交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186684}, {"id": 249390, "content": "买过裙子、画笔、秘密花园", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185654}, {"id": 249646, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185635}, {"id": 249391, "content": "怀孕后不能用的全新化妆品", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097424}, {"id": 249392, "content": "杯子...各种个样的杯子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185328}, {"id": 249393, "content": "没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805634}, {"id": 249649, "content": "因为经历，买了运动器材；给人或丢了衣物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699564}, {"id": 252209, "content": "电子琴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200547}, {"id": 249394, "content": "演唱会门票", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953514}, {"id": 249650, "content": "路过――碰到自己想要的对的，买买买！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185839}, {"id": 249139, "content": "旧书", "image": null, "praise_count": 671, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039682}]}